font-size:12pt;\"></span>\r\n	</p>\r\n	<p style=\"text-align:left;\">\r\n		<span style=\"font-family:&prime;宋体&prime;;font-size:12pt;font-weight:bold;\">五、学历认证</span><span style=\"font-family:&prime;宋体&prime;;font-size:12pt;font-weight:bold;\"></span>\r\n	</p>\r\n	<p style=\"text-align:left;text-indent:24pt;\">\r\n		<span style=\"font-family:&prime;宋体&prime;;font-size:12pt;\">本科考试13门课程。思想品德经鉴定符合要求者，颁发《人力资源管理》专业大学本科毕业证书。符合《中华人民共和国学位条例》规定的，授予工学学士学位。毕业证书：可在中国高等教育学生信息网站（http://chsi.com.cn）上查询认证。</span><span style=\"font-family:&prime;宋体&prime;;font-size:12pt;\"></span>\r\n	</p>\r\n	<p style=\"text-align:right;text-indent:24pt;\">\r\n		<span style=\"font-family:&prime;宋体&prime;;font-size:12pt;\"></span>\r\n	</p>\r\n</div>\r\n<p>\r\n	&nbsp;\r\n</p>', '2012-04-03 23:16:34', null, null, '23');
INSERT INTO `news` VALUES ('50', '14', '计算机应用软件', '<div>\r\n	<h4>\r\n		<span style=\"font-family:&prime;Cambria&prime;;font-size:15pt;font-weight:bold;\">2012</span><span style=\"font-family:&prime;宋体&prime;;font-size:15pt;font-weight:bold;\">年吉林大学计算机</span><span style=\"font-family:&prime;宋体&prime;;font-size:15pt;font-weight:bold;\">应用</span><span style=\"font-family:&prime;宋体&prime;;font-size:15pt;font-weight:bold;\">软件专业自学考试招生简章</span><span style=\"font-family:&prime;宋体&prime;;font-size:15pt;font-weight:bold;\"></span>\r\n	</h4>\r\n	<p style=\"text-indent:21.21pt;\">\r\n		<span style=\"font-family:&prime;Calibri&prime;;font-size:10.5pt;\">吉林大学是中国最早开展计算机科学技术研究的院校之一。<span>1981&nbsp;</span><span>年吉林大学计算机软件专业被批准为全国首批博士学位授权专业，&nbsp;</span><span>1985&nbsp;</span><span>年建立了全国首批计算机软件博士后科研流动站，</span><span>1988&nbsp;</span><span>年计算机软件专业又被批准为国家重点学科专业。&nbsp;</span></span><span style=\"font-family:&prime;Calibri&prime;;font-size:10.5pt;\"></span>\r\n	</p>\r\n	<p>\r\n		<span style=\"font-family:&prime;Calibri&prime;;font-size:10.5pt;\">计算机应用软件专业是为培养适应经济、社会发展的高素质人才而开设的一门应用型专业。《计算机应用软件专业》由吉林大学主考，为了帮助广大学员顺利取得学位证书，本中心面向全国招生。&nbsp;</span><span style=\"font-family:&prime;Calibri&prime;;font-size:10.5pt;\"></span>\r\n	</p>\r\n	<p style=\"margin-left:21.21pt;\">\r\n		<span style=\"font-family:&prime;Calibri&prime;;font-size:10.5pt;font-weight:bold;\">一、&nbsp;专业优势&nbsp;</span><span style=\"font-family:&prime;Calibri&prime;;font-size:10.5pt;font-weight:bold;\"></span>\r\n	</p>\r\n	<p style=\"margin-left:21.21pt;\">\r\n		<span style=\"font-family:&prime;宋体&prime;;font-size:10.5pt;\">1<span>、</span></span><span style=\"font-family:&prime;Calibri&prime;;font-size:10.5pt;\">取证时间短（</span><span style=\"font-family:&prime;宋体&prime;;font-size:10.5pt;\">高、</span><span style=\"font-family:&prime;Calibri&prime;;font-size:10.5pt;\">专起本只需一年）；&nbsp;</span><span style=\"font-family:&prime;Calibri&prime;;font-size:10.5pt;\"></span>\r\n	</p>\r\n	<p style=\"margin-left:21.21pt;\">\r\n		<span style=\"font-family:&prime;宋体&prime;;font-size:10.5pt;\">2<span>、</span></span><span style=\"font-family:&prime;Calibri&prime;;font-size:10.5pt;\">确保考试通过，成绩不过退还学费，无任何风险；&nbsp;</span><span style=\"font-family:&prime;Calibri&prime;;font-size:10.5pt;\"></span>\r\n	</p>\r\n	<p style=\"margin-left:21.21pt;\">\r\n		<span style=\"font-family:&prime;宋体&prime;;font-size:10.5pt;\">3<span>、</span></span><span style=\"font-family:&prime;Calibri&prime;;font-size:10.5pt;\">国家重点大学高含金量本科毕业文凭，国家认可；&nbsp;</span><span style=\"font-family:&prime;Calibri&prime;;font-size:10.5pt;\"></span>\r\n	</p>\r\n	<p style=\"margin-left:21.21pt;\">\r\n		<span style=\"font-family:&prime;宋体&prime;;font-size:10.5pt;\">4<span>、</span></span><span style=\"font-family:&prime;Calibri&prime;;font-size:10.5pt;\">符合条件者可以确保申请到国务院统一的学士学位；&nbsp;&nbsp;</span><span style=\"font-family:&prime;Calibri&prime;;font-size:10.5pt;\"></span>\r\n	</p>\r\n	<p style=\"margin-left:21.21pt;\">\r\n		<span style=\"font-family:&prime;宋体&prime;;font-size:10.5pt;\">5<span>、</span></span><span style=\"font-family:&prime;Calibri&prime;;font-size:10.5pt;\">超强师资力量，对在本中心报名的学员进行全程辅导，高通过率；&nbsp;</span><span style=\"font-family:&prime;Calibri&prime;;font-size:10.5pt;\"></span>\r\n	</p>\r\n	<p style=\"margin-left:21.21pt;\">\r\n		<span style=\"font-family:&prime;宋体&prime;;font-size:10.5pt;\">6<span>、</span></span><span style=\"font-family:&prime;Calibri&prime;;font-size:10.5pt;\">考前集中强化，周末上课，不脱产不耽误正常学习工作。&nbsp;</span><span style=\"font-family:&prime;Calibri&prime;;font-size:10.5pt;\"></span>\r\n	</p>\r\n	<p style=\"margin-left:21.21pt;\">\r\n		<span style=\"font-family:&prime;Calibri&prime;;font-size:10.5pt;font-weight:bold;\">二、&nbsp;招生对象&nbsp;</span><span style=\"font-family:&prime;Calibri&prime;;font-size:10.5pt;font-weight:bold;\"></span>\r\n	</p>\r\n	<p style=\"text-indent:21.21pt;margin-left:21.21pt;\">\r\n		<span style=\"font-family:&prime;Calibri&prime;;font-size:10.5pt;\">凡高中及同等学历者（含中专、中技、职高等），可报考专本科；属国民教育系列的各类专科或本科毕业生以及在校生（含自考在校生），可直接报读本专业本科。&nbsp;</span><span style=\"font-family:&prime;Calibri&prime;;font-size:10.5pt;\"></span>\r\n	</p>\r\n	<p style=\"margin-left:21.21pt;\">\r\n		<span style=\"font-family:&prime;宋体&prime;;font-size:10.5pt;font-weight:bold;\">三</span><span style=\"font-family:&prime;Calibri&prime;;font-size:10.5pt;font-weight:bold;\">、&nbsp;毕业待遇&nbsp;</span><span style=\"font-family:&prime;Calibri&prime;;font-size:10.5pt;font-weight:bold;\"></span>\r\n	</p>\r\n	<p style=\"text-indent:21.21pt;margin-left:21.21pt;\">\r\n		<span style=\"font-family:&prime;Calibri&prime;;font-size:10.5pt;\">成绩全部合格者，由吉林省自考委和吉林大学联合颁发教育部电子注册的本科毕业证书，国家承认学历，符合条件者可授予学士学位。同时，此证书也得到欧、美、日本等二十多个国家认可，出国留学深造、工作均有效。&nbsp;</span><span style=\"font-family:&prime;Calibri&prime;;font-size:10.5pt;\"></span>\r\n	</p>\r\n	<p style=\"margin-left:21.21pt;\">\r\n		<span style=\"font-family:&prime;宋体&prime;;font-size:10.5pt;font-weight:bold;\">四、</span><span style=\"font-family:&prime;Calibri&prime;;font-size:10.5pt;font-weight:bold;\">吉林大学计算机应用软件专业课程设置&nbsp;</span><span style=\"font-family:&prime;宋体&prime;;font-size:10.5pt;font-weight:bold;\"></span>\r\n	</p>\r\n	<p>\r\n		<span style=\"font-family:&prime;Calibri&prime;;font-size:10.5pt;\"></span>\r\n	</p>\r\n	<table style=\"border-collapse:collapse;\">\r\n		<tbody>\r\n			<tr>\r\n				<td style=\"border-bottom:#000000 0.5pt solid;border-left:#000000 0.5pt solid;border-top:#000000 0.5pt solid;border-right:#000000 0.5pt solid;\" valign=\"top\" width=\"75\">\r\n					<p>\r\n						<span style=\"font-family:&prime;Calibri&prime;;font-size:10.5pt;\">序</span><span style=\"font-family:&prime;宋体&prime;;font-size:10.5pt;\">号</span><span style=\"font-family:&prime;Calibri&prime;;font-size:10.5pt;\"></span>\r\n					</p>\r\n				</td>\r\n				<td style=\"border-bottom:#000000 0.5pt solid;border-left:#000000 0.5pt solid;border-top:#000000 0.5pt solid;border-right:#000000 0.5pt solid;\" valign=\"top\" width=\"75\">\r\n					<p>\r\n						<span style=\"font-family:&prime;Calibri&prime;;font-size:10.5p