<span style=\"font-family:&prime;Calibri&prime;;font-size:10.5pt;\"></span>\r\n	</p>\r\n	<p style=\"text-indent:21.21pt;margin-left:21.21pt;\">\r\n		<span style=\"font-family:&prime;Calibri&prime;;font-size:10.5pt;\">（<span>1</span><span>）</span><span>2</span><span>寸同底、蓝色、免冠彩色照</span><span>2</span><span>张；同版二寸蓝底照片电子版（原版）一张，像素</span><span>384×512</span><span>；保存为</span><span>JPG</span><span>格式；&nbsp;</span></span><span style=\"font-family:&prime;Calibri&prime;;font-size:10.5pt;\"></span>\r\n	</p>\r\n	<p style=\"text-indent:21.21pt;margin-left:21.21pt;\">\r\n		<span style=\"font-family:&prime;Calibri&prime;;font-size:10.5pt;\">（<span>2</span><span>）身份证原件扫描件，保存为</span><span>JPG</span><span>格式，小于</span><span>800K</span><span>；&nbsp;</span></span><span style=\"font-family:&prime;Calibri&prime;;font-size:10.5pt;\"></span>\r\n	</p>\r\n	<p style=\"text-indent:21.21pt;margin-left:21.21pt;\">\r\n		<span style=\"font-family:&prime;Calibri&prime;;font-size:10.5pt;\">（<span>3</span><span>）最高学历原件扫描件，保存为</span><span>JPG</span><span>格式，小于</span><span>800K</span><span>；&nbsp;</span></span><span style=\"font-family:&prime;Calibri&prime;;font-size:10.5pt;\"></span>\r\n	</p>\r\n	<p style=\"text-indent:21.21pt;margin-left:21.21pt;\">\r\n		<span style=\"font-family:&prime;Calibri&prime;;font-size:10.5pt;\">（<span>4</span><span>）学费、考务费。&nbsp;</span></span><span style=\"font-family:&prime;Calibri&prime;;font-size:10.5pt;\"></span>\r\n	</p>\r\n	<p style=\"margin-left:21.21pt;\">\r\n		<span style=\"font-family:&prime;宋体&prime;;font-size:10.5pt;font-weight:bold;\">六</span><span style=\"font-family:&prime;Calibri&prime;;font-size:10.5pt;font-weight:bold;\">、&nbsp;考试时间&nbsp;</span><span style=\"font-family:&prime;宋体&prime;;font-size:10.5pt;font-weight:bold;\"></span>\r\n	</p>\r\n	<p style=\"margin-left:21.21pt;\">\r\n		<span style=\"font-family:&prime;Calibri&prime;;font-size:10.5pt;\">每年的四月和十月&nbsp;</span><span style=\"font-family:&prime;Calibri&prime;;font-size:10.5pt;\"></span>\r\n	</p>\r\n	<p style=\"margin-left:21.21pt;\">\r\n		<span style=\"font-family:&prime;宋体&prime;;font-size:10.5pt;font-weight:bold;\">七、所获证书样本</span><span style=\"font-family:&prime;Calibri&prime;;font-size:10.5pt;font-weight:bold;\"></span>\r\n	</p>\r\n	<h3 style=\"text-align:center;margin-left:42.525pt;\">\r\n		<span style=\"font-family:&prime;宋体&prime;;font-size:10.5pt;font-weight:normal;\"></span>\r\n	</h3>\r\n	<h3 style=\"text-align:center;margin-left:42.525pt;\">\r\n		<span style=\"font-family:&prime;宋体&prime;;font-size:10.5pt;font-weight:normal;\"></span>\r\n	</h3>\r\n	<p>\r\n		<span style=\"font-family:&prime;Calibri&prime;;font-size:10.5pt;\"></span>\r\n	</p>\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; <img alt=\"\" src=\"/js/kindeditor/attached/image/20120425/20120425145519_95667.jpg\" />\r\n</div>\r\n<p>\r\n	&nbsp;\r\n</p>', '2012-04-03 23:16:34', null, null, '23');
INSERT INTO `news` VALUES ('324', '15', '经济与行政管理', '<div>\r\n	<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n		<span style=\"font-family:&prime;宋体&prime;;font-size:14pt;font-weight:bold;\">南京政治学院</span><span style=\"font-family:&prime;Calibri&prime;;font-size:14pt;font-weight:bold;\">经济与行政管理专业招生简章</span><span style=\"font-family:&prime;Calibri&prime;;font-size:12pt;\">&nbsp;</span><span style=\"font-family:&prime;宋体&prime;;font-size:14pt;\"></span>\r\n	</p>\r\n	<p style=\"text-align:left;\">\r\n		<span style=\"font-family:&prime;Calibri&prime;;font-size:12pt;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<span>高等教育自学考试是我国高等教育事业的重要组成部分</span><span>,</span><span>是中国特色社会注意教育制度的一项创举</span><span>.</span><span>他具有在职业余</span><span>,</span><span>灵活开放</span><span>,</span><span>宽进严出</span><span>,</span><span>严格规范的特点</span><span>,</span><span>无需入学考试</span><span>.</span><span>教育质量具有很高的社会信誉和国际认可度</span><span>.</span><span>享有国民教育同等学历资格</span><span>,</span><span>毕业证书由教育部统一监制</span><span>.</span><span>经全高等教育自学考试知道委员会和全军自学考试委员会批准。</span></span><span style=\"font-family:&prime;Calibri&prime;;font-size:12pt;\"></span>\r\n	</p>\r\n	<p>\r\n		<span style=\"font-family:&prime;Calibri&prime;;font-size:12pt;\">&nbsp;</span><span style=\"font-family:&prime;Calibri&prime;;font-size:12pt;\"></span>\r\n	</p>\r\n	<p>\r\n		<span style=\"font-family:&prime;Calibri&prime;;font-size:12pt;font-weight:bold;\">【专业特点】</span><span style=\"font-family:&prime;Calibri&prime;;font-size:12pt;\"></span>\r\n	</p>\r\n	<p>\r\n		<span style=\"font-family:&prime;Calibri&prime;;font-size:12pt;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<span>本专业分专科</span><span>(</span><span>设有经济管理&nbsp;行政管理两个方向</span><span>)</span><span>和独立本科段</span><span>,</span><span>是专本衔接</span><span>,</span><span>军地通用</span><span>,</span><span>服务军队</span><span>,</span><span>适应社会的复合型</span><span>,</span><span>应用型</span><span>,</span><span>适合广大干部和士官在职学习</span><span>.</span></span><span style=\"font-family:&prime;Calibri&prime;;font-size:12pt;\"></span>\r\n	</p>\r\n	<p>\r\n		<span style=\"font-family:&prime;Calibri&prime;;font-size:12pt;\">&nbsp;</span><span style=\"font-family:&prime;Calibri&prime;;font-size:12pt;\"></span>\r\n	</p>\r\n	<p>\r\n		<span style=\"font-family:&prime;Calibri&prime;;font-size:12pt;font-weight:bold;\">【报名办法】</span><span style=\"font-family:&prime;Calibri&prime;;font-size:12pt;\"></span>\r\n	</p>\r\n	<p>\r\n		<span style=\"font-family:&prime;Calibri&prime;;font-size:12pt;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<span>（一）报名条件：军队（含武警）干部，士官和在编职工，具有高中（中专）文化程度的可报考本专业专科段；具国家教育部门承认的专科以上的学历的可直接报考本专业本科段。</span></span><span style=\"font-family:&prime;Calibri&prime;;font-size:12pt;\"></span>\r\n	</p>\r\n	<p>\r\n		<span style=\"font-family:&prime;Calibri&prime;;font-size:12pt;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</span><span style=\"font-family:&prime;Calibri&prime;;font-size:12pt;\"></span>\r\n	</p>\r\n	<p>\r\n		<span style=\"font-family:&prime;Calibri&prime;;font-size:12pt;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<span>（二）报考程序：报考者需经团以上政治机关审批，必须在规定的报名时间内到指定地点办理报名手续。报名时间：</span><span>5</span><span>月份报考当年</span><span>10</span><span>月份开考的课程；</span><span>11</span><span>月份报考次年</span><span>4</span><span>月份开考的课程。考生报名时要填写《考试课程申报表》，并交纳考务管理及辅导费，教材费；首次报名的新生需填写《考生报名登记表》，交</span><span>6</span><span>张</span><span>1</span><span>寸近期免冠彩照，经考区、大单位考办审、汇总后统一报专业考委办公室注册，发给准考证。</span></span><span style=\"font-family:&prime;Calibri&prime;;font-size:12pt;\"></span>\r\n	</p>\r\n	<p>\r\n		<span style=\"font-family:&prime;Calibri&prime;;font-size:12pt;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</span><span style=\"font-family:&prime;Calibri&prime;;font-size:12pt;\"></span>\r\n	</p>\r\n	<p>\r\n		<span style=\"font-family:&prime;Calibri&prime;;font-size:12pt;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<span>（三）报考要求：考生根据每半年公布的考试科目，自愿选报考试课程，每人每次报考的课程不超过</span><span>4</span><span>门，同一半天内开考的课程，考生只能报考其中</span><span>1</span><span>门。</span></span><span style=\"font-family:&prime;Calibri&prime;;font-size:12pt;\"></span>\r\n	</p>\r\n	<p>\r\n		<span style=\"font-family:&prime;Calibri&prime;;font-size:12pt;\">&nbsp;</span><span style=\"font-family:&prime;Calibri&prime;;font-size:12pt;\"></span>\r\n	</p>\r\n	<p>\r\n		<span style=\"font-family:&prime;Calibri&prime;;font-size:12pt;font-weight:bold;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<span>经济与行政管理专业独立本科段考试课程设置表</span></span><span style=\"font-family:&prime;Calibri&prime;;font-size:12pt;\"></span>\r\n	</p>\r\n	<p>\r\n		<span style=\"font-family:&prime;Calibri&prime;;font-size:12pt;\">&nbsp;</span><span style=\"font-family:&prime;Calibri&prime;;font-size:12pt;\"></span>\r\n	</p>\r\n	<table style=\"border-collapse:collapse;\">\r\n		<tbody>\r\n			<tr>\r\n				<td style=\"border-bottom:#000000 0.75pt outset;border-left:#000000 0.75pt outset;border-top:#000000 0.75pt outset;border-right:#000000 0.75pt outset;\" valign=\"top\" width=\"295\" colspan=\"3\">\r\n					<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n						<span style=\"font-family:&prime;Calibri&prime;;font-size:12pt;font-weight:bold;\">必考课程</span><span style=\"font-family:&prime;宋体&prime;;font-size:12pt;\"></span>\r\n					</p>\r\n				</td>\r\n				<td style=\"border-bottom:#000000 0.75pt outset;border-left:#000000 0.75pt outset;border-top:#000000 0.75pt outset;border-right:#000000 0.75pt outset;\" valign=\"top\" width=\"312\" colspan=\"3\">\r\n					<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n						<span style=\"font-family:&prime;Calibri&prime;;font-size:12pt;font-weight:bold;\">选考课程</span><span style=\"font-family:&prime;宋体&prime;;font-size:12pt;\"></span>\r\n					</p>\r\n				</td>\r\n			</tr>\r\n			<tr>\r\n				<td style=\"border-bottom:#000000 0.75pt outset;border-left:#000000 0.75pt outset;border-top:#000000 0.75pt outset;border-right:#000000 0.75pt outset;\" valign=\"top\" width=\"43\">\r\n					<p>\r\n						<span style=\"font-family:&prime;Calibri&prime;;font-size:12pt;\">序号</span><span style=\"font-family:&prime;宋体&prime;;font-size:12pt;\"></span>\r\n					</p>\r\n				</td>\r\n				<td style=\"border-bottom:#000000 0.75pt outset;border-left:#000